SELECT `buyers`.`id`, `buyer_name`, `buyer_details`.`cc` as `cc`, SUM(buyer_details.buyer_qty) as total_qty, SUM(buy_cost) as buy_cost, SUM(buy_cost * buyer_details.buyer_qty) as total_buy_cost FROM `buyer_details` JOIN `buyers` ON `buyers`.`id` = `buyer_details`.`buyer` JOIN `purchase_items` ON `purchase_items`.`id` = `buyer_details`.`purchase_id` JOIN `lead_lists` ON `lead_lists`.`id` = `purchase_items`.`lead_id` WHERE `purchase_items`.`created_at` >= '2023-12-01 00:00:00' AND `purchase_items`.`created_at` <= '2023-12-29 23:59:59' AND `lead_lists`.`file_id` = '26' GROUP BY `buyer_details`.`cc`
